page_title: How to use Risks & Safety monitoring in Azure OpenAI Studio
page_description: Learn how to check statistics and insights from your Azure OpenAI content filtering activity.
chunk_content: Access Risks & Safety monitoringTo access Risks & Safety monitoring, you need an Azure OpenAI resource in one of the supported Azure regions: East US, Switzerland North, France Central, Sweden Central, Canada East. You also need a model deployment that uses a content filter configuration.Go to Azure OpenAI Studio and sign in with the credentials associated with your Azure OpenAI resource. Select the Deployments tab on the left and then select your model deployment from the list. On the deployment's page, select the Risks & Safety tab at the top.
